{"timestamp": "2026-06-26T23:39:45.193092", "user": "Explain: Train loss and validation loss can diverge.", "nova": "Train loss and validation loss can diverge."}
{"timestamp": "2026-06-26T23:39:45.193530", "user": "Explain: A gap can mean overfitting or limited generalization.", "nova": "A gap can mean overfitting or limited generalization."}
{"timestamp": "2026-06-26T23:39:45.194020", "user": "Explain: The model fits the seen data better than unseen data.", "nova": "The model fits the seen data better than unseen data."}
