{"timestamp": "2026-06-26T23:39:45.198494", "user": "Explain: Do not assume improvement from one sample.", "nova": "Do not assume improvement from one sample."}
{"timestamp": "2026-06-26T23:39:45.198935", "user": "Explain: A claim says a behavior change was caused by one file. What should be checked?", "nova": "A claim says a behavior change was caused by one file. What should be checked?"}
{"timestamp": "2026-06-26T23:39:45.199378", "user": "Explain: Training has many variables.", "nova": "Training has many variables."}
