{"timestamp": "2026-06-26T23:39:46.686128", "user": "Explain: Do not claim loss alone proves good output quality.", "nova": "Do not claim loss alone proves good output quality."}
{"timestamp": "2026-06-26T23:39:46.687880", "user": "Explain: A test fails after a tokenizer rebuild. What should be checked first?", "nova": "A test fails after a tokenizer rebuild. What should be checked first?"}
